        public Grade(java.lang.Double value,
     java.lang.String code)
        Construct a new Grade with the specified numerical value and string code. The value may be left null if this grade does not correspond to a numerical GPA value. For example, a grade such as an incomplete or withdrawal might not be associated with a number.
        Parameters:
        value - The grade received in a course
        code - An indentifying code for a course
